 Also, not to forget to take care of your body that nutures the mind. After all, the mind has a physical dependency too. Are you giving enough time for yourself or just keeping lingering with mundane tasks and crontolling things beyond your domain, which is the self. <hl>You don't control events or things, you manage them, understand this</hl>. How do you get better in managing and dealing with things that happen around you and what you do about it. What your actions are, that will make a difference to you and to the society as a whole, the world we live in.
